{"lemma":"حَظَّيْ","slug":"حَظَّيْ","root":"ح.ظ.ظ","root_slug":"ح-ظ-ظ","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ظ-ظ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حَظّ","root":"حظظ","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8406","n8431","n8435"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B8%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be fortunate, lucky"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"share, portion, lot (especially of something good)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"luck, good fortune"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"enjoyment, pleasure"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ح ظ ظ (ḥ ẓ ẓ). Compare Ugaritic 𐎈𐎑𐎚 (ḥẓt)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8406","headword_ar":"حَظِّىٌّ","root":"HZ","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZiY~N","text_ar":"حَظِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8431","headword_ar":"حِظًى","root":"HZw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiZFA","text_ar":"حِظًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuZowapN","text_ar":"حُظْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8435","headword_ar":"حَظِىٌّ","root":"HZw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZiYa","text_ar":"حَظِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fortunate"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"happy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in favour with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beloved by, and in high estimation with, others;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb, TA; *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occupying a high place"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rank"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the estimation of another"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"others"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZK","text_ar":"حَظٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (Har p. 623:) fem. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZiy~apN","text_ar":"حَظِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) applied to a woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in favour with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beloved by, and in high estimation with, her husband;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZaAyaA","text_ar":"حَظَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hiYa HaZiy~atiY","text_ar":"هِىَ حَظِيَّتِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She is my favourite"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iHodayi HaZaAyaAya","text_ar":"اـِحْدَيِ حَظَايَايَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of my favourites"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) For"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZiy~apN","text_ar":"حَظِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the vulgar say, erroneously, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoZiy~ap","text_ar":"مَحْظِيَّة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [meaning thereby"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A concubine;"},{"kind":"text","text":"in which sense"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZiy~apN","text_ar":"حَظِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used by late writers;] and making the pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAZiY","text_ar":"مَحَاظِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is also wrong. (TA.) Hence the prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaA A^aliy~apF","text_ar":"فَلَا اَلِيَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_il~aA HaZiy~apF","text_ar":"اـِلَّا حَظِيَّةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) explained in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alw","text_ar":"الو"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaZiY~u","text_ar":"الحَظِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eighth of the horses that are started together in a race."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 46.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","K","TA"]}]}}